Triggers
------------------------
SQL statements that are AUTOMATICALLY RUN when  a specific table changed

DELIMITER $$

CREATE TRIGGER must_be_adult
     BEFORE INSERT ON users FOR EACH ROW
     BEGIN
          IF NEW.age < 18
          THEN
              SIGNAL SQLSTATE '45000'
                    SET MESSAGE_TEXT = 'Must be an adult!';
          END IF;
     END;
$$

DELIMITER ;

it restricts age<18 to be inserted.
